3
00:00:06,610 --> 00:00:11,940
Hi, welcome to China Uncensored, I'm your
host Chris Chappell.

4
00:00:11,940 --> 00:00:15,240
So, you know who's incredibly awesome?

5
00:00:15,240 --> 00:00:16,340
You!

6
00:00:16,340 --> 00:00:18,420
Now there are some people out there who think,

7
00:00:18,420 --> 00:00:22,519
"Oh, what can I do? I can't make a difference
in this world."

8
00:00:22,519 --> 00:00:24,449
Not my viewers!

9
00:00:24,449 --> 00:00:29,320
Last week, when I found out that police in
China abducted my friend Ben Hedges' mother-in-law,

10
00:00:29,320 --> 00:00:31,220
I asked you to take action.

11
00:00:31,220 --> 00:00:36,590
"So get out your phones my precious 50-Cent
Army, and give police chief Yu Changjun a

12
