support in other ways, congratulations and

31
00:01:44,240 --> 00:01:45,040
thank you.

32
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:48,259
Together, we made things better in China.

33
00:01:48,259 --> 00:01:51,649
Once again I'm Chris Chappell, and this is
China Uncensored.

34
